message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Agroclimatic risk of Andean crops under CMIP6 scenarios in Imbabura, Ecuador: A reproducible Random Forest–Bayesian Network pipeline"
authors:
  - family-names: "Pinto Páez"
    given-names: "Víctor Hugo"
    affiliation: "Universidad San Gregorio de Portoviejo, Ecuador"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2026-03-14
license: MIT
