doi: "10.5281/zenodo.XXXXXXX"
abstract: >
  Complete reproducible pipeline for parish-level agroclimatic risk assessment
  of four Andean crops under CMIP6 scenarios across 42 parishes of Imbabura
  Province, Ecuador. Integrates Random Forest Species Distribution Models and
  Bayesian Networks following the IPCC AR6 risk framework.
keywords:
  - agroclimatic risk
  - Random Forest
  - Bayesian Networks
  - CMIP6
  - Imbabura
  - Ecuador
  - climate change adaptation
